# MIRAIKANAI baseline (Cursor rule)

- **Authority:** [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) is the shared baseline; resolve conflicts in favor of `AGENTS.md`.
- **Automation:** Use **PowerShell 7** only: `pwsh -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File tools/<script>.ps1`.
- **Scoped rules:** [`.cursor/rules/`](../../.cursor/rules/) (`mirakana-cmake-vcpkg`, `mirakana-cpp-engine`, `mirakana-editor-imgui-shell`, `mirakana-ai-agent-integration`).
- **Skills/subagents:** Thin pointers under [`.cursor/skills/`](../../.cursor/skills/); Cursor-only `gameengine-cursor-baseline` and `gameengine-plan-registry`; subagents under [`.cursor/agents/`](../../.cursor/agents/).
- **Drift check:** Before finishing implementation, compare changed behavior against owning agent surfaces and update stale guidance in the same task.
- **User language:** Respond in Japanese when the user writes Japanese; keep code, paths, and API names in ASCII.

Expanded procedures: [`docs/agent-operational-reference.md`](../../docs/agent-operational-reference.md), GitHub Flow and validation in `AGENTS.md`.
